You will upgrade your Austin 2025 Coin by completing the coin challenges. Earn a Souvenir Token every time you upgrade your Coin.

This viewer pass will pre-activate your Austin 2025 Coin with 3 Souvenir Tokens.

50% of the proceeds from the sale of this pass support the participating organizations.
